      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">25.702-3</ph> Remedies.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1686e8" class="- topic/p ">Upon the determination of a false certification under subsection <xref href="25.702-2.dita#FAR_25_702_2"
                  base="i1091211"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">25.702-2</xref>-</p>
         <ol id="d1656e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1678e15" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The contracting officer may terminate the contract;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1678e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The suspending official may suspend the contractor in accordance with the procedures in <xref href="Subpart_9.4.dita#FAR_Subpart_9_4"
                        base="i1115147"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  9.4</xref>; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1678e28" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            The debarring official may debar the contractor for a period not to exceed 3 years in accordance with the procedures in <xref href="Subpart_9.4.dita#FAR_Subpart_9_4"
                        base="i1115147"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  9.4</xref>.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
